      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bride of Charlie - Episode 5\n## The Complete Timeline & Romania Connection\n\n### \"The Players Are Now In Place\"\n\n**Big Questions:**\n- Erica's missing years - where is she?\n- Is she in Eastern Europe? Why?\n- Was Lorie in Afghanistan?\n- Is Lorie actually Vince Lombardi's descendant? (\"I actually think she is\")\n- Tyler Boyer out in Romania - what was he doing?\n\n### Main Revelations\n\n**1. Complete Erica Timeline 1988-2010**\n- Missing years: 2000-2002 (still unknown)\n- Lorie's E3 Tech: Operation Enduring Freedom (Afghanistan)\n- $2.4M from Army National Guard in 2008\n\n**2. Tyler Boyer in Romania 2010**\n- Same time as Black Sea Rotational Force\n- Modeling agency, parliament member\n- \"Romanian sloshed\" with girls\n- Married & LDS at the time\n\n**3. Jeffrey Epstein Romania Connection**\n- 2009: US military base established\n- Epstein immediately procuring Romanian models\n- Arizona State University connection\n\n**4. Rick Urbenbeck's License Loss**\n- Multiple mortgage fraud (led to financial crisis)\n- Deed fraud\n- \"Professional negligence\" not \"criminality\""
      }
    },
