      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Nancy Gerard Hall - Tesseract Principal\n\n### While Erica Was A Student\n\nNancy had **very strong military ties**\n\n### Her Father: Colonel Paul Tracy Gerard\n\n**Military Background:**\n- Member of Scottish Rite\n- Freemason at Fort Leavenworth, Kansas\n- Blue Masonic Lodge, Galesburg, Illinois\n- **Chief Military Law Enforcement Officer**\n- Seventh Army in Europe (Germany, Stuttgart, 1950s)\n\n**Candace's Note:**\n\"Maybe he knows where Jean-Michelle Trogno went. Maybe they cross paths.\"\n\n### Her Brother: Paul Tracy Gerard Jr.\n\n- Followed father's footsteps\n- **Major in the military** (1977)\n- Continued climbing ranks\n- Member of **Scabbard and Blade** (military honor society)\n\n### Her First Husband: Steven Edward Sample\n\n- Long line of military men\n- **Second Lieutenant in Air Force** when they married\n\n### Nancy's Role at Tesseract\n\n\"She's in charge of the curriculum and much more.\"\n\n**Candace's Speculation:**\n\"I think it's fair to wonder whether or not she approached that job with **military precision**.\"\n\n### The Pattern\n\n- Tesseract backed by Bush family & Waltons\n- Model designed by psychologists with Dr. Jerry France\n- Principal with deep military intelligence ties\n- Erica attended this school"
      }
