      "data": {
        "markdown": "## 1988-1999: Early Years\n\n### 1988\n\nErica born November 20th or 22nd (\"depending on who's telling the story\")\n\n### 1990\n\n**Dr. Jerry France** starts conducting research in Eastern Europe\n\n**Note:** \"I don't know if she is still married to Kent. We can't find marriage records between Lori and Kent, but we also could not locate divorce records between Dr. Jerry France and Kent.\"\n\n### 1991\n\nErica attends private daycare:\n- Walnut Corner, Cincinnati, Ohio\n- Corporate business building\n- Owned by Child Care Visions\n- Photo: Halloween 1991 (brink of 3rd birthday)\n\n### 1994-1995\n\nSt. Ursula Villa for kindergarten\n\n### 1995-1996\n\n**Tesseract School** (Paradise Valley)\n- First year at Tesseract\n- Parents Kent & Lori allegedly married (Marblehead, MA)\n- \"Cannot find a single shred of documentation\"\n\n### 1996-1998\n\nContinues at Tesseract\n\n### 1998-1999\n\n**Third Grade at Tesseract**\n\n**Lori & Kent file for divorce** (Cincinnati)\n- Kent already living in Arizona\n- Lori listed as living in Cincinnati\n\n### 1999\n\n**Lorie's LLC Explosion:**\n\n**December 1:** Virtual Registration International Inc.\n- With help of Rick & Donna Urbenbeck\n- \"Indicating she's going to be doing work overseas\"\n\n**September 24:** Intellment Incorporated\n\n**December 2:** Intellment International Inc. of Delaware\n\n\"She's getting ready to do business.\""
      }
