      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Where Is Erica?\n\n### 2000\n\n**Tesseract school goes bankrupt**\n- \"Millions are apparently missing\"\n- \"For-profit corporate drive to run public schools... full-blown meltdown\"\n\n**Erica:** Location unknown\n\n### 2001\n\n**9/11 & Operation Enduring Freedom**\n\n**The Question:**\n\"If Saudis allegedly drove planes into the World Trade Center, why are we immediately a couple of weeks later on **October 7th, 2001**, sending people to Afghanistan?\n\nIt's very confusing. None of it makes any sense. Don't try to understand corruption.\"\n\n**Lorie's E3 Tech Company:**\n- Used for Operation Enduring Freedom\n- According to its current website\n- Eventually wins award for contributions\n\n**The Question:**\n\"Did Erica go overseas with her mother during those years? Maybe in 2001.\n\nI don't even know if Lori went overseas.\n\nI'm just telling you that according to their own website E3, they received an award for whatever they were doing for that operation.\"\n\n### 2002\n\n**Erica:** Still no idea which school\n\n### The APB\n\n**Candace's Call:**\n\"If you went to school with Erica France anywhere in the United States from the years **2000 to 2002**, we would like to hear from you.\"\n\n**Note:** Initially thought St. Ursula Villa, but people with yearbooks confirmed she's NOT there during these years."
      }
