        "markdown": "## 2003-2007\n\n### 2003\n\n**Lorie forms:** Intellment of Arizona LLC (January 9)\n\n### 2005\n\n**Erica documented at Notre Dame Prep:**\n- Playing basketball\n- Pageant world\n- First runner up: National American Miss Arizona\n\n**MOST CRUCIAL: Lorie's Government Money**\n\n**IMAT Laboratories:**\n- Listed in House bill budget\n- Receiving money from **Department of Homeland Security**\n- \"Could not find formation docs\"\n- \"Maybe related to Intellment - could be shortened from Intellment Laboratories\"\n\n**Question:** \"What is she doing for them?\"\n\n### 2006\n\n**Erica:**\n- Wins National American Miss Teen Pageant\n- Travels to DC\n- Meets Senator John Kyl\n- Presents plans to Rep. JD Hayworth\n- Gets involved in Andrea's Closet charity (Winslow hospital)\n\n**The Winslow Story Problem:**\n\nErica claims: \"We love stopping here. Come through many times on way to basketball games.\"\n\n**Expert Email:**\n- 80% of Arizona population in Maricopa County\n- Winslow 3 hours from Scottsdale\n- Structure of teams: would only go to Winslow **2 times max** in 4 years\n\n**Red Flag:** \"Mother is involved in this immediately flagging this as weird. How did she get involved with this hospital?\"\n\n**Also:** \"She says she loves to do charity work **abroad**. That would imply Erica has already been abroad.\"\n\n### 2007\n\n- Graduates Notre Dame Prep\n- Miss America Teen\n- Begins basketball at Regis University\n- **Major:** Business Administration\n- Lorie's A-Tech International cancelled (tax filing), will reinstate later"
      }
