        "markdown": "## Erica Missing, Lorie Gets Millions\n\n### Erica's Status\n\n**2007-2008 School Year at Regis:**\n- \"Locked away like Cinderella\"\n- \"Reading her Bible\"\n- \"Only seeing her pastor\"\n- **Majoring:** Business Administration\n- Regis player bio still available\n\n**2008-2009:**\n- Assumed continuing studies online (\"kind assumption\")\n- Future she'll claim: majored in political science \"from the beginning\"\n- \"That's not true\"\n- Takes **5 years total** to graduate college\n\n### LORIE RECEIVES $2.4 MILLION\n\n**Army National Guard → IMAT Laboratories**\n\nAmount: **$2,400,000**\n\n**Purpose:** J3, J6\n- Cyber security\n- Cyber operations\n\n### The Evolution\n\n**Candace's Summary:**\n\n\"Erica already, via her mother, who she claims raised her as a single mom. She didn't, unless maybe her mindset it was the single mom cuz **Erica was over on a base with her mother**.\n\nBut we now know that during this year, this crucial year where Erica is missing, her mother is going to wind up having received $2.4 million.\n\nI mean, this woman:\n- From a model\n- To a secretary  \n- To now she's getting all of this money for tech\n\nIt's interesting.\""
