        "markdown": "## Romania Military Base = Epstein Procurement\n\n### The Timing\n\n**2009:** Romanian government agrees to US military base\n\n**Same year:** Jeffrey Epstein begins procuring women from Romania\n\n### The Evidence\n\n**Email Quote:**\n\"Here is information for the girl from Romania who will receive **$10,000**.\"\n\n**Headlines:**\n\"Several Romanian women named in newly released Epstein case files.\"\n\n**Pattern:**\n\"There have been headlines about how often he refers to Romania throughout his emails.\n\nThere is no question.\"\n\n### The Arizona State Connection\n\n**Important Note:**\n\"The number one university that he seems to be involved with is **Arizona State University**.\n\nWhich Erica will eventually graduate from.\"\n\n### Candace's Summary\n\n\"For the purposes of right now, just know that Jeffrey Epstein:\n\nWe have emails going back to **2009**.\n\n**Right when this base gets established.**\n\nAnd suddenly he is interested in procuring **models from Romania**.\n\nOkay, lock that into your mind.\"\n\n### The Questions\n\n- Why Romania specifically?\n- Why immediately after base established?\n- Connection to modeling agencies?\n- Arizona State University role?\n- Erica's eventual graduation from ASU?"
