      "data": {
        "markdown": "## 2010: Multiple Suspicious Activities\n\n### Loyola Marymount (Allegedly)\n\n**Erica claims:** Junior year (Fall 2009 - Spring 2010)\n- Can't find her in yearbook/graduation list\n- No one remembers her in class\n- Could have attended online\n- \"Given amount of travel, probably did take a lot of classes online\"\n\n### January 6, 2010: Dr. Jerry Creates LLC\n\n**Luminarius LLC**\n- With daughter Deborah Himsil (the one she had at 14)\n- Deborah \"following mommy's footsteps\" into psychology\n- **Another charter school company**\n\n### The Charter School Question\n\n**Candace's Theory:**\n\n\"What are they doing with these charter schools?\n\nWhat would be the benefit?\n\n**You being in charge of schools, you could create records for anybody actually.**\n\nYou would literally be able if you wanted to and you had some people who were maybe illegal and you needed to get them into school pretty quickly in elementary school, **it would be good to control a fleet of charter schools**.\n\nI'm not saying that's the case with Luminarius Group, but I'm finding this theme to be interesting.\"\n\n**Pattern:** Corruption of charter schools in Arizona\n- Begins with Tesseract\n- Continues to move\n\n### November 2010: November Renaissance Film\n\n**What It Was:**\n- Eventually put trailer on Kickstarter\n- **Never came out**\n- About: **Corporate espionage, spies working on behalf of global government**\n\n**Red Flags:**\n- Actors/directors affiliated with **Fort Huachuca & Sierra Vista**\n- \"That is an intel base\"\n- \"How did Erica get this role?\"\n- \"How is she doing this in addition to her studies?\"\n- \"A little too on the nose for me\"\n\n### Also 2010: LLC with Boyfriend\n\n**Table Four LLC**\n- With Tyler Sanford\n- He's catcher for LA Angels\n- Later featured in her \"My Kind of Crazy\" music video (2013)\n- \"Erica always dating people that have some level of fame\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "eeeeeeee-eeee-4eee-8eee-eeeeeeeeeeee",
