      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Lorie Reinstates, Marines Deploy\n\n### 2010: Lorie Reinstates A-Tech International\n\n**Remember:**\n- First got in trouble (not filing tax returns)\n- Then Lorie moves to reinstate in 2010\n- **AZ Tech International back on the table**\n\n### May 17, 2010: Marines to Romania\n\n**Black Sea Rotational Force 10:**\n\nOfficial ceremony at Romania's **Mihail Kogălniceanu Airfield**\n\n**Official Statement:**\n\"Marines, sailors, and sailors of the Black Sea Rotational Force 2010 officially kicked off their **three-month engagement** in the Black Sea region.\"\n\n**Timing:** May through end of summer\n\n### Interesting Detail: Reno, Nevada\n\n\"What's incredibly interesting is in particular, a lot of those people are coming from **Reno, Nevada** of all places.\"\n\n### The Official Banner\n\n**They claim:**\n\"Allegedly there because they're going to promote **regional stability**.\"\n\n**Candace's Take:**\n\"We have a way with words, I will say, in the West:\n- Regional stability\n- Spreading democracy\"\n\n### The Reality: Colonel Otto Busher\n\n**Accusations:**\nRunning a **brothel and human trafficking ring**\n\n**Timeline:** 2010-2015\n- From the very year base established\n- Through 2015\n\n**Important Note:**\n\"Yes, Erica will come into contact with Colonel Otto Busher.\n\nWe're not going to focus on that today.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ffffffff-ffff-4fff-8fff-ffffffffffff",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Tyler Boyer in Romania 2010",
      "position": {
        "x": 1180,
        "y": 1360
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 840,
      "color": "#bf360c",
      "ports": [
