          "position": {
            "side": "bottom",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## \"I'm Sorry, WHAT?\"\n\n### Tyler's Timeline\n\n**May through end of summer 2010:**\nTyler Boyer makes appearance in Romania\n\n**Purpose:** \"To work with the Romanian Parliament\"\n\n**Exact same timeframe:** Black Sea Rotational Force 10 deployment\n\n### The Conversation (Receipts)\n\n**Tyler's Message:**\n\n\"I went to Romania to do some work with a **senator in the parliament** there.\n\nAnd he was friends, meaning the senator in Romania was friends with **this guy that owned a modeling agency** and took me to the beach [Constanța] for 4 days and legit slept collectively like 10 hours.\"\n\n**Friend responds:** \"Oh, I was at a lake...\"\n\n**Tyler continues:**\n\n\"But yeah, **these girls were crazy** and I got completely **Romanian sloshed**.\n\nAnd it got very interesting. Haha.\"\n\n**Candace:** \"This is the Tyler I know. Everybody knows who Tyler is.\"\n\n### The Problems\n\n**1. He Was Married:**\n\"Pretty sure Tyler was married in 2010. Check the records. I think he was married to his first wife in 2010.\"\n\n**2. He's LDS:**\n\"Also, isn't he LDS? Doesn't that mean he's not supposed to be drinking?\n\nOh, who cares? It's all for appearances anyways. **Super Christian company.** Who cares what they're actually doing?\"\n\n### More From Tyler\n\n**About the whiskey:**\n\"They had this homemade whiskey that was like, I can't explain it, but yeah, **the girls were wow, both of them**.\"\n\n**Candace:** \"I told you he's a sexual deviant. There's just so much out there. It's crazy.\"\n\n**Tyler's final comment:**\n\"I can drink a lot so I don't pass out or get weird or anything. Ha.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a1a1a1a1-a1a1-4a1a-8a1a-a1a1a1a1a1a1",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "The Questions Tyler Won't Answer",
      "position": {
        "x": 1180,
        "y": 2260
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 680,
      "color": "#311b92",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "content",
          "position": {
            "side": "top",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## What Was He Doing?\n\n### The Unanswered Questions\n\n**1. Who was the person in Romanian Parliament?**\n\n\"Who was the person in Romanian Parliament that he was there to see?\"\n\n**2. What was the modeling agency?**\n\n\"What was the name of the modeling agency?\n\nI am dying to know because it's gonna get real interesting now, right?\"\n\n### Erica \"Can't Remember\"\n\n**How She Knows Tyler:**\n\n\"Erica just can't remember. She can't remember how she knows him. She can't remember how she met him.\"\n\n**What She Told Candace:**\n\n\"She said to me, 'Maybe it was through a senator.'\n\nSpecifically, that's what she said to me in person.\n\nShe said it might have been through a senator.\n\nI think it could have been through a senator.\n\n**I think it definitely could have been through a senator.**\"\n\n### The Connection\n\n**Candace's Theory:**\n\n\"Honestly, the vibes are vibing here.\n\nI find that **you both have a little something to do with what's going on in Romania**.\n\nAs soon as America gets there and establishes a base, which is going to become pretty much **synonymous, if you speak to Romanians, with trafficking models in Romania**.\n\nDo you know Jeffrey Epstein, Tyler? Did you guys come across each other? Because **he was dealing with models from Romania, too**.\"\n\n### The Request\n\n\"I know this is — I know they're just carrying on Charlie's legacy and everybody grieves differently and it might not be the time to ask.\n\nI'd really like to know **what model agency that Romanian Parliament member was working with** that Tyler had a fun night out with.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b2b2b2b2-b2b2-4b2b-8b2b-b2b2b2b2b2b2",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Rick Urbenbeck License Loss EXPOSED",
      "position": {
        "x": 600,
